_sText:
My second Counter-Strike Source map, and somehow was able to get it done before February. Takes place in a Russian Military silo in Siberia, includes a nuke and other stuff. Thank you for playing my map. You may need to generate your own nav for bot support.

WARNING:
Just to make sure, but this map was not made to support or mock anything relating to current events. This was just made because I didn't want to make another city map. If you actually think that, then you are a goddamn retard.
